As of 2010, the population of Creola was 213 with 80 households which 65% are owned, 30% are rented, and 5% are unoccupied. The median household income is $44,499. 62% of the population are married couples with 44% of them have children. Males make up 48% of the total population while females make up the other 52%.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.coldwellbanker.com/real_estate/home_search/la/Creola | title = Creola Overview | accessdate = March 8, 2013}}</ref>

